        "id": "t1780361091260",
        "title": " Testing - Exit Triage with edge cases",
        "desc": "Set up a test scenario:\n\nAdd a test member \"Edge Case Tester\"\nCreate 3 tasks assigned to them\nMake Edge Case Tester the manager of one of those tasks (open task → set manager)\nMake Edge Case Tester the delegator (assignedBy) of another task\nNow Archive them via Exit Triage:\n\nReassign 1 task to someone else\nPark 1 task to Unassigned\nCancel 1 task\n\n\nIn the Delegations section, transfer ownership to someone\nIn the Approvals section, transfer manager to someone\nClick Archive\nThen reload\n✅ Verify: reassignments stuck, parked task in Unassigned, cancelled task is cancelled, delegations transferred, manager transferred",
